resources.description: This paper deals with the problem of robust H∞ control for network systems with time delay and uncertainties. The aim is to design a delay-dependent robust output feedback controller which ensures both robust asymptotic stability and prescribed level of H∞ performance for all admissible uncertainties.
resources.name: Robust H∞ Output Feedback Control for Dynamic Network Systems
